    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行将一些银行家在大修中进行短期保留</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/hsbc-places-some-bankers-on-short-term-retention-amid-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行（HSBC Holdings Plc）将其一些投资银行家置于短期保留协议上，因为它在新任首席执行官乔治·埃尔希德里（Georges Elhedery）领导的广泛大修中陷入了各种业务，据熟悉此事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/hsbc-places-some-bankers-on-short-term-retention-amid-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 00:33:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔首席执行官信号表明他会坚持有争议的铸造计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/intel-ceo-signals-that-he-ll-stick-with-contentious-foundry-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将到来的英特尔公司（Intel Corp.）首席执行官Lip-bu Tan表示，他将坚持他的前任计划为其他公司制作筹码的计划，即使他发誓要从过去的错误中学习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/intel-ceo-signals-that-he-ll-stick-with-contentious-foundry-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 00:29:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
